CREATE TABLE DIM_BILLING_TIME ( ID NUMBER(10) PRIMARY KEY, ID_WITH_QUARTER_MONTH NUMBER(10), DAILY_DATE DATE NOT NULL , MONTH_BEGIN_DATE DATE NOT NULL, MONTH_END_DATE DATE NOT NULL , MONTH VARCHAR2(4), MONTH_ID VARCHAR2(30), MONTH_INT NUMBER (6), YEAR NUMBER (4), KEY_TYPE NUMBER(1) ) NOLOGGING

insert into DIM_BILLING_TIME SELECT to_number(to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'YYYYMMDD')) id ,to_number(to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'YYYYQMM')) id_with_quarter_month , to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'DD-MON-YY') daily_date , to_char(trunc(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'MONTH'),'DD-MON-YY') month_begin_date , to_char(last_day(date_from+(LEVEL-1)),'DD-MON-YY') month_end_date , to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'MON') month , to_number(to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'YYYY')) || '/' || to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'MON') month_id , to_number(to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'MM')) month_int , to_number(to_char(date_from+(LEVEL-1),'YYYY')) year , 0 key_type FROM (SELECT from_dt date_from ,to_dt date_to ,to_dt-from_dt days_between FROM (SELECT to_date('01-JAN-2000','DD-MON-YYYY') from_dt , to_date((select to_char(sysdate,'dd-mon-yyyy') from dual),'DD-MON-YYYY') to_dt FROM dual)) CONNECT BY (LEVEL-1) <= (days_between)

insert into DIM_BILLING_TIME SELECT to_number(to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) id, to_number(to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'Q') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) ID_WITH_QUARTER_MONTH, ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)) daily_date, ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)) begin_date, lAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1))) end_date, to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MON') MONTH, to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || '/' || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MON') MONTH_ID, to_number( to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) MONTH_INT, EXTRACT( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1))) YEAR, 1 KEY_TYPE
FROM (SELECT from_dt date_from ,to_dt date_to ,MONTHS_BETWEEN (to_dt,from_dt) days_between FROM (SELECT to_date( 'JAN-2000','MON-YYYY') from_dt , to_date((select to_char(add_months(sysdate,1),'mon-yyyy') from dual),'MON-YYYY') to_dt FROM dual)) CONNECT BY (LEVEL-1) <= days_between
